01:05:10,910 --> 01:05:13,710
Text Ji Wan and Su Bin.

907
01:05:14,700 --> 01:05:16,720
Change the next item?

908
01:05:16,720 --> 01:05:18,030
What do you mean?

909
01:05:18,030 --> 01:05:21,100
I have an idea.

910
01:05:22,280 --> 01:05:24,420
I'll add a guest.

911
01:05:24,420 --> 01:05:26,240
Guest?

912
01:05:30,160 --> 01:05:32,200
 

913
01:05:32,200 --> 01:05:34,410
 Come home by six. 

914
01:05:35,600 --> 01:05:38,700
 I need to tell you something important. Be there. 

915
01:05:40,180 --> 01:05:41,860
Did I get caught?

916
01:05:41,860 --> 01:05:43,880
Gosh, did I get caught?

917
01:05:44,720 --> 01:05:46,970
Yes.

918
01:05:46,970 --> 01:05:49,110
This wasn't working, anyway.

919
01:05:49,110 --> 01:05:51,640
I should come clean

920
01:05:51,640 --> 01:05:54,510
and take just one beating.

921
01:05:54,510 --> 01:05:57,800
But his punches are too strong.

922
01:06:10,700 --> 01:06:13,680
 Aigoo, what's gotten into you? 

923
01:06:13,680 --> 01:06:16,430
How did you all three come home together?

924
01:06:16,430 --> 01:06:19,520
How long has it been since we ate together?

925
01:06:19,520 --> 01:06:21,960
Hyung told us to come home early.

926
01:06:21,960 --> 01:06:23,700
He called us.

927
01:06:23,700 --> 01:06:26,750
You did, Ji Hyeok? Why?

928
01:06:26,750 --> 01:06:28,950
Is something going on with you?

929
01:06:28,950 --> 01:06:30,870
Finish dinner first.

930
01:06:30,870 --> 01:06:33,200
Ji Hyeok, tell us now.

931
01:06:33,200 --> 01:06:35,360
What is it?

932
01:06:35,360 --> 01:06:38,340
Why did you call Ji Wan and Su Bin?

933
01:06:38,340 --> 01:06:39,540
Did you guys cause trouble?

934
01:06:39,540 --> 01:06:40,640
- No.
- No.

935
01:06:40,640 --> 01:06:43,950
No. I need to tell you something.

936
01:06:43,950 --> 01:06:46,820
You're free for lunch this Thursday, right?

937
01:06:46,820 --> 01:06:48,560
Yes.

938
01:06:48,560 --> 01:06:50,240
Mom is probably free.

939
01:06:50,240 --> 01:06:52,970
Ji Wan, Su Bin, cancel plans if you have any.

940
01:06:52,970 --> 01:06:54,450
- Okay.
- Okay.

941
01:06:54,450 --> 01:06:58,890
Ji Hyeok, you need to tell us
what's going on first.

942
01:06:58,890 --> 01:07:00,830
I'd like you...

943
01:07:00,830 --> 01:07:04,630
to meet the parents of my fiancée.

944
01:07:06,630 --> 01:07:08,130
I'm...

945
01:07:09,120 --> 01:07:10,820
getting married.

946
