949
01:07:46,890 --> 01:07:52,140
 ♫ Under the quiet night sky ♫ 

950
01:07:52,140 --> 01:07:56,600
 ♫ Looking at the moon shining brightly ♫ 

951
01:07:56,600 --> 01:08:05,680
 ♫ I take a step forward slowly,
hoping to reach you ♫ 

952
01:08:05,680 --> 01:08:08,150
 I'm not asking you to approve this marriage. 

953
01:08:08,150 --> 01:08:12,310
 When did you decide to have the wedding? 

954
01:08:12,310 --> 01:08:14,690
 You didn't get angry at all. 

955
01:08:14,690 --> 01:08:16,100
 Didn't it hurt your ego? 

956
01:08:16,100 --> 01:08:19,560
 I expect great and refreshing designs. 

957
01:08:19,560 --> 01:08:21,960
 How's 30 million as the design fee? 

958
01:08:21,960 --> 01:08:23,020
 I'm getting married. 

959
01:08:23,020 --> 01:08:24,110
 You sure you won't regret it? 

960
01:08:24,110 --> 01:08:25,350
 Ji Hyeok is getting married. 

961
01:08:25,350 --> 01:08:28,530
 This was the reason we were incompatible. 

962
01:08:28,530 --> 01:08:30,480
 I'm sorting things out for the last time. 

963
01:08:30,480 --> 01:08:33,160
 To send away my unrequited love. 

964
01:08:33,160 --> 01:08:34,870
 Here comes the groom. 

965
01:08:34,870 --> 01:08:40,700
 ♫ I'll take one step at a time
and always wait for you ♫ 

